~bGetting Advanced Help~B

If you have read all the help topics on the home page in the recommended order
and would like to get more detailed information about the editor's commands and
features, you can use the Advanced Help System.  This system uses menus and
pop-up windows for all help pages so that you can view information and return
to your editing session quickly.  The ~#uC-h C-h~U key sequence is not used (and not
bound).

To enter the Advanced Help System, simply enter a numeric prefix to the "help"
command, for example, ~#uC-u ESC ?~U.


<home>    <exit>
